All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AnalyticsCounter
read a symptoms file and write a file containing the occurrences of each symptom sorted alphabetically. use entry file symtoms.txt and create result.out by default, with option to change it by specifying other names in the command line
FileNames
Class containing the names of input and output files
IResultWriter
Will read the TreeMap of symptoms and occurrences and write the file of the results
ISymptomReader
Anything that will read symptom data from a source The important part is, the return value from the operation, which is a list of strings, that may contain many duplications The implementation does not need to order the list
ReadSymptomDataFromFile
Simple brute force implementation
WriteResultToFile
Will read the TreeMap of symptoms and occurrences and write the file of the results
